The mechanism in one sentence
When a test runs an action, the live POM locator is tried first; if it fails, findWithFallback runs, and the two page-vs-db comparisons happen there: STEP 1 checks if the DB primary still resolves (same → leave), and if not, after healing locates the element, refreshStaleElement recomputes the page primary and string-compares it to the DB primary (different → write primary + smart_locators + meta together).
